item.title: Pajers
item.description:
Pajers

The importance of having a resilient business: Over 25% of businesses never reopen after a natural disaster. Put another way, one in four businesses are forced to close permanently. In our lifetimes, we face unprecedented challenges posed by climate change and the increased risk of natural disasters.
